</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">You could have a model of Harvard Busi=
ness School that is like:</p><ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding=
-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;">=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Harvard =
Business School teaches you skills that would make you good at running a co=
mpany.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">There are lots of companies=
 that could use those skills.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">But =
you don=E2=80=99t want to run those companies, because they make, like, bal=
l bearings.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;"><em>You=C2=A0</em>want=
 to run a=C2=A0<em>fancy=C2=A0</em>company; you want to run a hedge fund or=
 a tech startup or something.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Mean=
while, the people currently running the ball bearings company would not be =
all that excited about=C2=A0<em>you</em>, a fresh-faced business school gra=
duate who has never run anything, coming in to run their company, even if y=
ou did learn a lot of useful skills at Harvard.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-=
bottom: 5px;">Therefore various industries exist whose principal business i=
s=C2=A0<em>laundering=C2=A0</em>ball bearings companies=C2=A0into opportuni=
ties that appeal to Harvard Business School graduates. You wrap the ball be=
arings company in a name like =E2=80=9Cprivate equity=E2=80=9D and suddenly=
 it is legible to the Harvard students, so they flock to it.</li>=09<li sty=
le=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Those industries are also in the business of get=
ting the ball bearings companies to accept the Harvard Business School grad=
uates, which in practice means not so much=C2=A0=E2=80=9Cmake the ball bear=
ings company excited about its new Harvard CEO=E2=80=9D but rather=C2=A0=E2=
=80=9Cbuy the ball bearings company and install new management.=E2=80=9D</l=
i></ol><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I don=E2=80=99t think this model is=C2=
=A0exactly<em>=C2=A0</em>right or anything, but I think there=E2=80=99s som=
ething to it. We have <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/cl=
ick/35821175.259288/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGV=
