<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[3] Is this problem symmetrical? It=E2=80=99s =
possible that the sellers are systematically crypto traders who don=E2=80=
=99t know that verbal contracts are binding, while the buyers are systemati=
cally claims traders who are used to this system and always close their dea=
ls. But it=E2=80=99s also the case that FTX claims went pretty monotonicall=
y up, and I suppose it=E2=80=99s possible that if they had instead gone dow=
n some of the sellers would be suing reluctant buyers now.</p>
